Source: pg-jieba
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cmake, g++
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/jaiminpan/pg_jieba

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-jieba
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-jieba
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Chinese full-text search parser for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_jieba embeds the cppjieba tokenizer and provides text search parsers,
 configurations, dictionaries, and query segmentation support.
